## Data Flows

### Inbound Data Flows

[From external systems to our system]

**Ejemplo:**
- Customer browses → Web Portal sends search queries → System returns products
- Payment confirmation → Stripe sends webhook → System updates order status

### Outbound Data Flows

[From our system to external systems]

**Ejemplo:**
- Order created → System sends inventory update → Supplier system updates stock
- User purchase → System sends data → Analytics warehouse

### Bidirectional Data Flows

[Both directions]

**Ejemplo:**
- Order sync with warehouse → Warehouse sends updates, we send confirmations

